ied to post a link below, it did not highlight.  Anyway, I have posted an apology to the Spheres of Honor for trampling on their FG raid in my zeal to reach Naggy's lair.  I tried to make it very clear that this was a rogue operation, and not sanctioned by the VH.  I also made it clear that it was the result of serveral snippets of very bad information that I had received.  For everyone else that may be in a similar sitation one day, always send a tell to teh raid leader of a posted raid to ensure that the raid is indeed off before interefering in their reservation.  Again, the full apology is at the Brell boards.<br>
